--- Refactor: FIND-603 — Remove duplicate CORRUPTED_BANNER_STYLES from designTokens.ts ---

Problem: Two exports named CORRUPTED_BANNER_STYLES existed in the same feature:
  - designTokens.ts:114-120: fontSize "14px", border "1px solid #dd5b00" (SPEC-WRONG)
  - corruptedBanner.ts:18-24: fontSize "16px", border DESIGN_TOKENS.whisperBorder (SPEC-CORRECT per REQ-014)
  AppShell.svelte was importing from designTokens.ts (the wrong one), while the unit test
  imported from corruptedBanner.ts (the right one). Tests passed but production was wrong.

Fix applied:
  1. designTokens.ts: Removed CORRUPTED_BANNER_STYLES export (lines 110-120 replaced with
     a tombstone comment directing importers to corruptedBanner.ts).
  2. AppShell.svelte: Already updated in Phase 2b to import CORRUPTED_BANNER_STYLES from
     ./corruptedBanner.js (the canonical source). No further change needed here.

Single-source-of-truth after fix:
  - One export: corruptedBanner.ts exports CORRUPTED_BANNER_STYLES
  - One import in production code: AppShell.svelte imports from ./corruptedBanner.js
  - Unit test (corrupted-banner.unit.test.ts) imports from ./corruptedBanner — consistent

Verification: grep confirms no file imports CORRUPTED_BANNER_STYLES from designTokens.ts.

